## Description 
This app is made to help the avid gym fanatic track their workout routines. With this app one could add exercises to previous workout plans or new ones as desired. The workouts are divided into resistance or cardio. A prompt of fields will be displayed after choosing either of the prior choices. The fields have categories such as; type, name, set, weight, sets, distance, and duration just to name a few. This app uses mongoose to store the data as supposed to MySQL. The front-end was provided for us and only the back-end was left in order to tie it together.
